{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <h2>最新天文台天氣報告｜未來五天香港天氣預報</h2>\n    <p>天文台展望，明日仍然較涼及間中有驟雨。隨後一兩日驟雨減少，氣溫逐步回升，天色較為明朗。</p>\n    <table>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>日期</cell>\n        <cell>5月4日(一)</cell>\n        <cell>5月5日(二)</cell>\n        <cell>5月6日(三)</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最高溫度</cell>\n        <cell>25度</cell>\n        <cell>24度</cell>\n        <cell>27度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最低溫度</cell>\n        <cell>21度</cell>\n        <cell>21度</cell>\n        <cell>23度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>風向及級數</cell>\n        <cell>北至東北風4至5級。</cell>\n        <cell>東風4至5級。</cell>\n        <cell>東風4級，離岸間中5級。</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>濕度</cell>\n        <cell>70-95%</cell>\n        <cell>80-95%</cell>\n        <cell>70-90%</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>顯著降雨概率</cell>\n        <cell>中</cell>\n        <cell>中</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>天氣</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨。天氣稍涼。稍後雨勢較為頻密，局部地區有雷暴。</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲，間中有驟雨。初時局部地區有雷暴。天氣稍涼。</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲，初時有一兩陣微雨，日間部分時間天色明朗。</cell>\n      </row>\n    </table>\n    <table>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>日期</cell>\n        <cell>5月7日(四)</cell>\n        <cell>5月8日(五)</cell>\n        <cell>5月9日(六)</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最高溫度</cell>\n        <cell>28度</cell>\n        <cell>30度</cell>\n        <cell>29度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最低溫度</cell>\n        <cell>24度</cell>\n        <cell>25度</cell>\n        <cell>24度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>風向及級數</cell>\n        <cell>東至東南風4級。</cell>\n        <cell>南至東南風3級。</cell>\n        <cell>微風2級，漸轉東北風3級。</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>濕度</cell>\n        <cell>70-90%</cell>\n        <cell>65-90%</cell>\n        <cell>70-95%</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>顯著降雨概率</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n        <cell>中低</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>天氣</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲，初時有一兩陣驟雨。日間短暫時間有陽光。</cell>\n        <cell>部分時間有陽光。稍後有幾陣驟雨。</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨。</cell>\n      </row>\n    </table>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-03T23:12:58.898327+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":484,"images":0,"source":"GoTrip","fallback":"none"}}